<div class="user-guide-page container">
  <h1><%= page.title %></h1>
  <p class="lead"><%= page.description %></p>

  <div class="guide-screenshot mb-4">
    <img src="<%= page.screenshotUrl %>" alt="<%= page.title %> screenshot" class="img-fluid border" />
  </div>

  <h2>Alternate names</h2>
  <p>Alternate names allow your club to be shown under different titles (for example, abbreviated names or historical names). This is useful for searching and display on event pages.</p>

  <h3>Adding an alternate name</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Click <em>Add Alternate Name</em>.</li>
    <li>Enter the alternate name and save.</li>
    <li>The new name will appear in search results and on club listings.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Removing or editing alternate names</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>To edit, click the edit icon next to the alternate name.</li>
    <li>To remove, click delete and confirm. Deleted names are removed from search and display.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-3"><a href="<%= page.url %>">Open the Alternate Names page</a></p>
  <p><a href="/user-guide">Back to guide index</a></p>
</div>
